{"data":[{"name":"84:1","price":"૧) જ્યારે આકાશ ફાટી જશે.","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ ٱنشَقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5885,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"gu","meta":{"transliteration":"idhā al-samāu inshaqqat ","translations":["When","the sky","is split asunder","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["idhā","al-samāu","inshaqqat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,3560],[3,3560,5515]]}},{"name":"84:2","price":"૨) અને  પોતાના  પાલનહારનો  આદેશ માની લેશે,  અને તેના માટે જરૂરી છે કે તે આવું જ કરે.","arabic":"وَأَذِنَتۡ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5886,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"gu","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-adhinat lirabbihā waḥuqqat ","translations":["And has listened","to its Lord","and was obligated","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-adhinat","lirabbihā","waḥuqqat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,2210],[3,2210,3655]]}},{"name":"84:3","price":"૩)  અને જ્યારે જમીન ફેલાવી દેવામાં આવશે.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡأَرۡضُ مُدَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5887,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"gu","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-arḍu muddat ","translations":["And when","the earth","is spread","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-arḍu","muddat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,610],[2,610,1510],[3,1510,2715]]}},{"name":"84:4","price":"૪) અને તેમાં જે કંઇ પણ છે, તેને તે બહાર ફેંકી દેશે અને ખાલી થઇ જશે.","arabic":"وَأَلۡقَتۡ مَا فِيهَا وَتَخَلَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5888,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"gu","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alqat mā fīhā watakhallat ","translations":["And has cast out","what","(is) in it","and becomes empty","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alqat","mā","fīhā","watakhallat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1070],[2,1070,1430],[3,1430,2260],[4,2260,3965]]}},{"name":"84:5","price":"૫)   અને  પોતાના  પાલનહારનો  આદેશ માની લેશે,  અને તેના માટે જરૂરી છે કે તે આવું જ કરે.","arabic":"وَأَذِنَتۡ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5889,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"gu","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-adhinat lirabbihā waḥuqqat ","translations":["And has listened","to its Lord","and was obligated","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-adhinat","lirabbihā","waḥuqqat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1040],[2,1040,2220],[3,2220,3805]]}},{"name":"84:6","price":"૬)  હે  માનવી  !  તું  પોતાના  પાલનહાર પાસે  પહોચતા  સુધી સતત કોઈ મહેનત કરતો રહીશ, અહી સુધી કે તેની પાસે જતો રહીશ.","arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِنَّكَ كَادِحٌ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ كَدۡحٗا فَمُلَٰقِيهِ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5890,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"gu","meta":{"transliteration":"yāayyuhā al-insānu innaka kādiḥun ilā rabbika kadḥan famulāqīhi ","translations":["O","mankind","Indeed, you","(are) laboring","to","your Lord","(with) exertion","and you (will) meet Him","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["yāayyuhā","al-insānu","innaka","kādiḥun","ilā","rabbika","kadḥan","famulāqīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2600],[2,2600,4850],[3,4850,6230],[4,6230,7350],[5,7350,7890],[6,7890,8750],[7,8750,10220],[8,10220,13585]]}},{"name":"84:7","price":"૭) પછી  જેનું  કર્મનોંધ તેના જમણા  હાથમાં આપવામાં આવશે.","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ بِيَمِينِهِۦ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5891,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"gu","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-ammā man ūtiya kitābahu biyamīnihi ","translations":["Then as for","(him) who","is given","his record","in his right (hand)","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-ammā","man","ūtiya","kitābahu","biyamīnihi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1840],[2,1840,2210],[3,2210,2990],[4,2990,4260],[5,4260,6055]]}},{"name":"84:8","price":"૮)   તેનો હિસાબ તો ખુબ જ સરળ લેવામાં આવશે.","arabic":"فَسَوۡفَ يُحَاسَبُ حِسَابٗا يَسِيرٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5892,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"gu","meta":{"transliteration":"fasawfa yuḥāsabu ḥisāban yasīran ","translations":["Then soon","his account will be taken","an account","easy","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["fasawfa","yuḥāsabu","ḥisāban","yasīran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,820],[2,820,1890],[3,1890,3080],[4,3080,5275]]}},{"name":"84:9","price":"૯)  અને તે પોતાના ઘરવાળાઓ તરફ ખુશી ખુશી પાછો ફરશે.","arabic":"وَيَنقَلِبُ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ مَسۡرُورٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5893,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"gu","meta":{"transliteration":"wayanqalibu ilā ahlihi masrūran ","translations":["And he will return","to","his people","happily","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["wayanqalibu","ilā","ahlihi","masrūran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1990],[2,1990,3820],[3,3820,4880],[4,4880,6845]]}},{"name":"84:10","price":"૧૦) હા ! જે વ્યક્તિને તેનો કર્મનોંધ તેની પીઠ પાછળથી આપવામાં આવશે.","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ وَرَآءَ ظَهۡرِهِۦ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5894,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"gu","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ammā man ūtiya kitābahu warāa ẓahrihi ","translations":["But as for","(him) who","is given","his record","behind","his back","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ammā","man","ūtiya","kitābahu","warāa","ẓahrihi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1910],[2,1910,2300],[3,2300,3090],[4,3090,4450],[5,4450,6780],[6,6780,8105]]}},{"name":"84:11","price":"૧૧) તો તે નષ્ટતા પોકારશે.","arabic":"فَسَوۡفَ يَدۡعُواْ ثُبُورٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5895,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"gu","meta":{"transliteration":"fasawfa yadʿū thubūran ","translations":["Then soon","he will call","(for) destruction","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["fasawfa","yadʿū","thubūran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,800],[2,800,1550],[3,1550,3215]]}},{"name":"84:12","price":"૧૨) અને ભડકે બળતી જહન્નમમાં દાખલ થશે.","arabic":"وَيَصۡلَىٰ سَعِيرًا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5896,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"gu","meta":{"transliteration":"wayaṣlā saʿīran ","translations":["And he will burn","(in) a Blaze","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["wayaṣlā","saʿīran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,970],[2,970,2695]]}},{"name":"84:13","price":"૧૩) તે  પોતાના ઘરવાળાઓ સાથે (દુનિયામાં) ઘણો  ખુશ હતો.","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ فِيٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ مَسۡرُورًا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5897,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"gu","meta":{"transliteration":"innahu kāna fī ahlihi masrūran ","translations":["Indeed, he","had been","among","his people","happy","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["innahu","kāna","fī","ahlihi","masrūran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1690],[2,1690,2400],[3,2400,3990],[4,3990,5020],[5,5020,6925]]}},{"name":"84:14","price":"૧૪) તે સમજતો હતો કે  તે ક્યારેય મારી તરફ પાછો નહિ આવે.","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ ظَنَّ أَن لَّن يَحُورَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5898,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"gu","meta":{"transliteration":"innahu ẓanna an lan yaḥūra ","translations":["Indeed, he","(had) thought","that","never","he would return","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["innahu","ẓanna","an","lan","yaḥūra",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1540],[2,1540,3130],[3,3130,3460],[4,3460,3900],[5,3900,7915]]}},{"name":"84:15","price":"૧૫) કેમ નહી આવે, નિ:શંક તેનો પાલનહાર તેને સારી રીતે જોઇ રહ્યો હતો.","arabic":"بَلَىٰٓۚ إِنَّ رَبَّهُۥ كَانَ بِهِۦ بَصِيرٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5899,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"gu","meta":{"transliteration":"balā inna rabbahu kāna bihi baṣīran ","translations":["Yes","Indeed","his Lord","was","of him","All-Seer","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["balā","inna","rab